ze carbohydrates.</s><s>Utilize peptone or amino acids and produce acetate and butyrate as the major fermentation products.</s><s>The cell-wall peptidoglycan contains lysine as the diagnostic diamino acid.</s><s>The type species is <em>Anaerosphaera aminiphila.</em></s></p></content></protolog>